description: After a chance encounter with their squadmate Luck, Magna and Vanessa go to extremes in a struggle to free their friend from a crazed elf's clutches.
title: Lightning of Rage vs. Friends

description: Yami reflects on the time he spent working alongside William Vangeance, captain of the Golden Dawn, and the secret mission they were given. Can the two strong-willed mages work together to make the Wizard King proud?
title: Yami and Vangeance

description: The Royal Knights take some time to rest before preparing for their attack against the Eye of the Midnight Sun. But when an enemy spy is discovered, the mission is moved up! Is Asta ready for his biggest test of strength yet?

input: Storming the Eye of the Midnight Sun's Hideout!!!
the Eye of the Midnight Sun's Hideout!!!
Eye of the Midnight Sun's Hideout!!!

title: Storming the Eye of the Midnight Sun's Hideout!!!

description: The Black Bulls learn why their home base keeps changing shape; that same power is put to the test against members of the Eye of the Midnight Sun.
title: Crazy Magic Battle

description: Fierce fighter Mereoleona takes on Rhya of the Third Eye and his wide range of formidable Copy Magic spells as Zora tries to figure out how they work.
title: Mereoleona vs. Ryha the Disloyal

description: The battle rages on between the Wizard King and Licht, who holds a kingdom's worth of innocent people hostage. Julius recalls his greatest motivation.
title: Julius Novachrono

description: Yami rushes to Julius's side as the Wizard King's battle with Licht draws to a close. Yuno's team approaches the center of the terrorist's hideout.
title: New Future

description: The vice-captain of the Crimson Lion Kings, now a reincarnated elf, turns on his squad mates with powerful Air Magic. A mighty beast awakens at last.
title: The Sleeping Lion

description: Royal Knights and disgraced mages alike encounter friends and squad mates whose bodies have been taken over by reincarnated elves. Can Black Asta help?
title: Overwhelming Disadvantage

description: Even remote little Hage Village is not immune from the chaos overtaking the Clover Kingdom. Asta and Yuno are determined to fight for their hometown.

input: The Lives of the Village in the Sticks
Lives of the Village in the Sticks
of the Village in the Sticks

title: The Lives of the Village in the Sticks

description: When Langris insults the Black Bulls, Asta, Charmy, and Finral prove that they're just as capable on the battlefield! Meanwhile Yami demands that William reveal what's under his mask. Will he unmask a terrible secret or just a tragic story?
title: Behind the Mask

description: Up against three of the Eight Shining Generals, Yuno and the Golden Dawn prove the Clover Kingdom will not go down easily! But nothing compares to the magic used by the captain of the Golden Dawn, William Vangeance!
title: Whoever's Strongest Wins

description: As Fanzell continues his search for Domina, he has an unfortunate run-in with the rest of the Black Bulls. After settling the misunderstanding, they're happy to send him on his way…that is, until the base is attacked!
title: The Man Named Fanzell, Continued

description: Asta is swept up by Noelle, Finral, Zell, and Domina and suddenly taken to the Witches' Forest! When they manage to sneak in, they discover Vanessa at the feet of the Queen who claims they will all fall.
title: Infiltration

description: The battle heats up as Asta and the Black Bulls face the furious flamed-up Fana! But when her fire gets too hot and starts affecting Vanessa and Finral's magic, it's up to Noelle to use her water magic to cool things off!
title: Flames of Hatred

description: Fana reveals that there's a magic stone in the Witches' Forest but before Asta and his friends find it, Ladros reappears! When the Diamond Mage consumes Salamander's power, Asta may not stand a chance.
title: Bettering One Another

description: An unexpected reunion could lead to turnaround in this heated battle! Asta and Mars fight side-by-side to go up against Fana and the powerful Salamander.
title: The Promised World

description: A devilish power awakens within Asta. Does he have the strength to control it, or will it inevitably be his undoing?
title: Not in the Slightest

description: The power to control fate is within everyone. Vanessa discovers a new power that will save her friends and stop the wicked Queen of Witches.
title: The Red Thread of Fate

description: Time for a festival—the Star Festival that is! The Magic Knights all gather to celebrate the stars each squad has earned. But when Asta invites Kahono and Kiato, he and Noelle end up on a double date with them!
title: A Fun Festival Double Date

description: Things at the star festival are starting to heat up. Jack, of the Green Praying Mantis', challenges Yami to a deadly battle of selling the most food! Who will make it to the end of the festival?

input: Battle to the Death?! Yami vs. Jack
to the Death?! Yami vs. Jack

title: Battle to the Death?! Yami vs. Jack

description: The Captain of the Blue Rose Knights is ready to show her thorns when she starts attracting the wrong kind of attention at the festival.
title: The Briar Maiden's Melancholy

description: Asta, Yuno, and Noelle get dragged to the Crimson Lion Kings' training camp when Mereoleona gets her paws on them. This is no trip to the hot springs, it's a fiery death trap in a volcanic belt! And only those with mana can survive.
title: The Uncrowned, Undefeated Lioness

description: It's time for the tournament to get…beautiful? As Magna and Sol deal with the beautiful-obsessed Kirsch, the Black Bulls are proving they're a squad worth reckoning with.
title: Fierce Battle

description: Asta is fired up for their first match, but Xerx seems more interested in a nap! Looks like it's up to just Asta and Mimosa to carry the team. Luckily, Mimosa is bringing some brand-new skills to the fight!
title: Flower of Resolution

description: The battles continue to heat up as Luck and Klaus prove that hard work pays off!  But in the final round of the first half, Yuno and Noelle will face Solid Silva—Noelle's brother!
title: Bad Blood

description: Rill surprises everyone by entering the competition! Are the knights ready to face a Magic Knight captain? Or will Rill make everyone question a captain's capabilities? Meanwhile, Luck and Klaus get ready to start their first match.
title: Mage X

description: It's time for round two—Asta's team versus Magna, Sol, and Kirsch! When Kirsch goes big right off the bat, it's time for Asta to show how hard he's been working to master his own abilities. But can he get Xerx to finally work with the team?
title: Peasant Trap

description: After taking care of Kirsch, it's time for Asta and Magna to face off! Magna is ready to show he's been getting stronger and surprises Asta with a brand-new technique. Can Team B protect the crystal or is this their final match?
title: Mister Delinquent vs. Muscle Brains

description: When the Black Bulls step in to stop Langris from dealing a final blow to Finral, the Wizard King demands the fight between Asta and Langris happen in the semi-finals! It's Team B versus Team G to see who is superior, and who will survive!

input: The Life of a Certain Man

title: The Life of a Certain Man

description: While things are heating up in the tournament, Charmy is having her own dangerous encounter! Well, in her dreams at least. Get ready for an episode filled with charm…y, la!

input: Clover Clips: The Nightmarish Charmy Special!

title: Clover Clips: The Nightmarish Charmy Special!

title: Together in the Bath

title: Smiles, Tears

title: The Battle for Clover Castle

description: Fueled by Charmy's magical meals, Asta's team detours to defend Hecairo on their way to the royal capital and picks up a trio of most unlikely allies.

input: Path of Revenge, Path of Atonement

title: Path of Revenge, Path of Atonement

description: Noelle must think outside the box to gain the upper hand in the pitched battle at House Silva. Thoughts of her mother help her push past her limits.
title: Battlefield Dancer

title: Spatial Mage Brothers

title: The Eyes in the Mirror

title: Humans Who Can Be Trusted

title: The Ultimate Natural Enemy

title: Breaking the Seal

description: A flashback to the truth behind the first Wizard King's battle against the demon serves as prelude for a new face joining the fight against the devil.

input: A Reunion Across Time and Space

title: A Reunion Across Time and Space

description: Foes turned allies, knights, captains, and rivals alike push past their limits, finding new abilities as the epic devil battle reaches a fever pitch.
title: The Final Attack

description: Asta's Black Asta form does him no favors in the court of Damnatio Kira. It's up to a powerful few to save Asta's head from the chopping block.

input: As Pitch Black as It Gets

title: As Pitch Black as It Gets

description: Secre reflects on Patry's reincarnation and that of his fellow elves, the utter havoc they wreaked, how it all ended, and what her future might hold.
title: Nero Reminisces... Part Two

description: An expedition to the Heart Kingdom uncovers a beautiful, mana-rich land that is a little less than welcoming. Finral resolves to turn over a new leaf.
title: To the Heart Kingdom!

title: Clues

description: The trainees split into teams hoping to find a certain magic item in the Yultim dungeon--if the gigantic spider lurking there doesn’t find them first.
title: The Lion Awakens, Continued

description: Mereoleona grabs a few fiery handsful of Black Bulls to join her squad in a training session at Yultim Volcano, where several surprises await them.
title: The Lion Awakens

description: Asta, Yuno, Noelle, and Secre are dispatched to Hage Village, where Sister Lily presses the quartet into service at the village's newest institution.
title: A New Resolve

description: The Wizard King summons the Magic Knight captains to brief them on the alliance with the Heart Kingdom against Megicula and to plan their next steps.

input: The New Magic Knight Squad Captains' Meeting
New Magic Knight Squad Captains' Meeting

title: The New Magic Knight Squad Captains' Meeting

description: Asta and Noelle arrive at the Fuegoleon residence for a secretive gathering, unreasonable requests, and an all-out brawl between two heavy hitters.
title: Those Who Have Been Gathered

description: Finral asks Asta to help him break his own curse: his flirty nature. Blue Rose Knights and Black Bulls come together for a meeting--or is it a mixer?

Who Has My Heart, My Mind, and Soul
Has My Heart, My Mind, and Soul
My Heart, My Mind, and Soul

title: The One Who Has My Heart, My Mind, and Soul

description: The Black Bulls are (mostly) training in Raquey when Kahono and Kiato approach them for help defending an Underwater Temple that's under attack.
title: A Black Deep-Sea Story

description: Charmy apprentices with the royal chef in the hopes of upping her food game, while Gordon goes out in search of regained strength through solitude.

input: Charmy's Century of Hunger, Gordon's Millennium of Loneliness
Century of Hunger, Gordon's Millennium of Loneliness
of Hunger, Gordon's Millennium of Loneliness

title: Charmy's Century of Hunger, Gordon's Millennium of Loneliness

description: While visiting his father Zara's grave, Zora encounters a commoner youth who's determined to join the Magic Knights despite upper-class opposition.
title: In Zara's Footsteps

description: The Queen of Witches agrees to teach Vanessa magic to buff her squadmates--but only if she can drive the huge magic beasts out of the queen's domain.
title: A Witch's Homecoming

description: Julius enlists the aid of an expert in dark magic items and sends two Magic Knight captains to investigate reports of bandits near a distant village.
title: A Favor for Julius

description: A group of masked vigilantes calling themselves the Devil Vanishers is ambushing and abducting those they believe to be in service to the devil.
title: Those Remaining

description: Asta is in a deep sleep as a contingent of Black Bulls searches for the kidnapped Marie and Secre. Julius offers both a promising lead and a warning.
title: The Tilted Scale

description: Marie and Secre face execution in the public square for their purported dealings with the devil. The Magic Knights spring into action to rescue them.
title: Rescue

description: The search for Marie and Secre continues, stymied by villagers who resent the Magic Knights' inaction during the elf invasion. Time for a new plan.

input: Those Who Wish for the Devil's Demise
Who Wish for the Devil's Demise

title: Those Who Wish for the Devil's Demise

description: The Golden Dawn is dispatched to Saussy to defeat a bevy of beastly boars, then it's off to the Kiten region to defend a dungeon beset by bandits.
title: The Golden Family

description: Asta and friends search for Secre, abducted by a group of magic-poor people who believe the power of the devil can change their lives for the better.
title: Those Who Worship the Devil

description: Asta approaches the Devil Believers, intent on talking things out as they near the Spade Kingdom--and the mighty devil dwelling within its borders.
title: Prepared to Die

description: Secre recalls Prince Lumiere's plans for Clover Kingdom equality. Asta and friends check in with Lolopechka as they prepare to train with her mages.

input: Two Things We Need to Find

title: Two Things We Need to Find

description: A cohort of the mightiest Magic Knight captains intercepts the Devil Believers to dissuade them from their journey. Bow and Dazu learn their fates.

input: Becoming the Light That Shines Through the Darkness
the Light That Shines Through the Darkness
Light That Shines Through the Darkness

title: Becoming the Light That Shines Through the Darkness

description: Grey asks her Black Bull squadmates for help overcoming her shyness. The Blue Rose Knights train for the Spade Kingdom fight. Julius gets an idea.
title: The Maidens' Challenge

description: Two teams of Magic Knight captains put on an outrageous display of power as they're pitted against each other in a new take on the Royal Knights test.

input: Clash! The Battle of the Magic Knights Squad Captains!
The Battle of the Magic Knights Squad Captains!
Battle of the Magic Knights Squad Captains!
of the Magic Knights Squad Captains!

title: Clash! The Battle of the Magic Knights Squad Captains!

description: Last year's new recruits attend the Magic Knights Entrance Exam and reflect on the year gone by. Vangeance returns something that belongs to Yuno.
title: To Tomorrow!

description: The Magic Knight captains recommend candidates for Spirit Guardian training in the Heart Kingdom, and several outstanding mages are promoted in rank.
title: The Chosen Ones

description: With Yuno rumored to be the next Golden Dawn vice-captain, the current vice-captain challenges the new Senior Magic Knight, First Class to a face-off.
title: Vice-Captain Langris Vaude

description: The contingent of Magic Knights from the Clover Kingdom arrives in the Heart Kingdom, where they're paired up with ace Spirit Guardians for training.
title: The 5 Spirit Guardians

description: Asta hits a wall in his training, while Mereoleona puts Yami through the wringer. A group of resistance members attempts to escape the Spade Kingdom.
title: Awakening Powers

description: As part of his training, Asta tells his instructor how he earned his grimoire, learned to read ki, and began to channel and control the devil's power.
title: Five-Leaf Clover

description: The newly trained Magic Knights spring into action to save exploited villagers in a Spade Kingdom fortress as it approaches the Heart Kingdom border.

input: The Beginning of Hope and Despair

title: The Beginning of Hope and Despair

description: Asta and friends must stop one of their own who's running amok in the Heart Kingdom. A man from the Spade Kingdom arrives in Hage looking for Yuno.
title: Quiet Lakes and Forest Shadows

description: Ralph shares the circumstances of Yuno's birth - and how he wound up at the church in Hage. Tragedy strikes the Golden Dawn HQ while Yuno is away.

input: The Messenger from the Spade Kingdom

title: The Messenger from the Spade Kingdom

description: Yuno battles ruthless Spade Kingdom mages at a devastated Golden Dawn HQ, soon realizing that even his mighty magic is no match for the Dark Triad.
title: Zenon's Power

description: As the Dark Triad's Vanica enters the Heart Kingdom, brother Dante visits the Black Bulls' hideout to meet Yami - but finds Asta and friends instead.
title: The Great War Breaks Out

description: Grey recalls her unhappy childhood and a fateful encounter. Yami takes on the ruthless Dante, while Luck faces off against a marauding Dark Disciple.

input: Dante vs. the Captain of the Black Bulls
vs. the Captain of the Black Bulls
the Captain of the Black Bulls

title: Dante vs. the Captain of the Black Bulls

description: With some Spirit Guardians out of commission, Charmy and Leopold step in to tangle with two more Dark Disciples. Lolopechka has an unexpected visitor.
title: Battlefield: Heart Kingdom

description: Once Lolopechka realizes what will happen if the Dark Triad are triumphant, she and the women in her palace go all-out against Vanica - and Megicula.
title: Water Crusade

description: Noelle finally comes face to face with the devil who killed her mother. Yami battles a seemingly invincible Dante as Asta and friends can only watch.
title: Captain: Yami Sukehiro

description: Vanica departs for the Spade Kingdom, hostage in tow. Asta communes with his inner devil for a diabolical boost in the fight with Yami against Dante.
title: Black Oath

description: The Magic Knight captains hold an emergency meeting, where a cryptic newcomer presents a plan to defeat the Dark Triad and rescue Yami and Vangeance.
title: Stirrings of the Strongest

description: Time's running out: our heroes must find new might in just two days. Nacht subjects Asta to an esoteric rite that pits him against his very own devil.
title: The Devil-Binding Ritual

description: The odds are stacked high against Asta, who must conquer his devil if he hopes to retain his power: the fight of a lifetime is just around the corner.
title: The Faraway Future
